OL,3,CGovernment's #113m demand 'will harm
OL,4,Cfamilies'
OL,6,FA Government plan for Stormont's new
OL,7,Fpower-sharing executive to raise #113
OL,8,Fmillion in additional funds over the
OL,9,Fnext year will cause "harm to hard-
OL,10,Fpressed families, households and
OL,11,Fbusinesses", Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,12,FArchibald has said.
OL,14,FThe Treasury has offered to write off
OL,15,Falmost #600million of Stormont debt,
OL,16,Fconditional on the Executive raising
OL,17,Fthe amount and producing a plan to
OL,18,Fdeliver sustainable finances.
