OL,3,CGovernment's #113m demand 'will harm
OL,4,Cfamilies'
OL,6,FThe stipulation is a key element of a
OL,7,F#3.3billion financial package drawn up
OL,8,Fby the Government to support the
OL,9,Freturn of devolution in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FChief Secretary to the Treasury Laura
OL,13,FTrott confirmed details of the
OL,14,Fsettlement in a letter to Ms Archibald
OL,15,Fon Tuesday.
OL,17,FBut the new finance minister responded
OL,18,Fto Ms Trott, stating that she has
OL,19,F"serious concerns" over the details
OL,20,Fpublished by the Treasury and has
OL,21,Fasked for an urgent meeting.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@RO]
