OL,3,CGovernment's #113m demand 'will harm
OL,4,Cfamilies'
OL,6,FThe government described it as a
OL,7,F"significant, fair and generous"
OL,8,Fpackage.
OL,10,FBut Ms Archibald said: "Ministers are
OL,11,Funited and speak with one voice in the
OL,12,Fneed to invest and reform our public
OL,13,Fservices.
OL,15,F"Making the write-off of the #559
OL,16,Fmillion for debt repayment conditional
OL,17,Fon the publication and implementation
OL,18,Fof a sustainability plan is not
OL,19,Facceptable.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@`O]rD@XOUwD@AOU
