OL,4,Cfamilies'
OL,6,F"It is our strong view that these
OL,7,Fdebts exist primarily due to the
OL,8,Funderfunding of public services.
OL,10,F"The executive has already given a
OL,11,Fcommitment to the British Government
OL,12,Fto develop a sustainability plan with
OL,13,Fa pre-requisite that the right level
OL,14,Fof funding is provided.
OL,16,F"The government's timescale requiring
OL,17,Fthis to be published by May 2024 is
OL,18,Fcompletely unrealistic.
