OL,6,F"It is essential that the executive is
OL,7,Fafforded adequate time to give proper
OL,8,Fconsideration to this important
OL,9,Fmatter."
OL,11,FShe added: "To expect this funding to
OL,12,Fbe generated in such a short space of
OL,13,Ftime can only serve to cause more harm
OL,14,Fto hard-pressed families, households
OL,15,Fand businesses.
OL,17,F"Our message to Westminster is simple.
