OL,6,F"The executive should be given time
OL,7,Fand space to develop and agree a
OL,8,Fproperly thought-through
OL,9,Fsustainability plan that will put our
OL,10,Ffinances on a more stabilised footing."
OL,12,FThe government said the financial
OL,13,Fsettlement included a requirement for
OL,14,Fthe executive to deliver a balanced
OL,15,Fbudget for 2024/25 that includes a
OL,16,Fminimum of #113m raised through
OL,17,Flocally generated income.
OL,19,FThe #113m equates to a 15% rise on the
OL,20,Fportion of household rates bills that
OL,21,Fis set by the executive.
