OL,6,FThe Executive currently raises around
OL,7,F#1.65billion a year through rates and
OL,8,Fother revenue-raising forms.
OL,10,FRates bills are calculated by adding
OL,11,Fthe regional rate (set by the
OL,12,Fexecutive) to the district rate (set
OL,13,Fby local councils) and multiplying
OL,14,Fthat by individual property values.
