OL,6,FHowever, it has made clear that its
OL,7,Foffer to write off a #559m debt
OL,8,Faccrued due to overspends of Stormont
OL,9,Fbudgets during the two-year Stormont
OL,10,Fimpasse is conditional on ministers
OL,11,Fproducing, by May this year, a
OL,12,Fsustainability plan that includes
OL,13,Frevenue raising measures and
OL,14,Fefficiency initiatives.
