OL,6,FThe broad shape of the financial
OL,7,Fpackage was already known after it was
OL,8,Fhammered out in negotiations between
OL,9,Fthe local parties and the Government
OL,10,Fat Hillsborough Castle before
OL,11,FChristmas when power sharing was still
OL,12,Fin cold storage.
OL,14,FThe #113m revenue raising ask was put
OL,15,Fto the parties during those
OL,16,Fnegotiations.
OL,18,FDetails on the financial package
OL,19,Foutlined in the letter to Ms Archibald
OL,20,Finclude:
