OL,6,FThe Government said it has also
OL,7,Fcommitted to open discussions with the
OL,8,Fexecutive on a "new fiscal framework"
OL,9,Ffor Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland Secretary Chris
OL,12,FHeaton-Harris welcomed confirmation of
OL,13,Fthe settlement's details.
OL,15,F"This package tackles the immediate
OL,16,Fbudget pressures facing the restored
OL,17,Fexecutive and allows it to take action
OL,18,Fto rapidly stabilise public services,
OL,19,Fwhile increasing opportunities for
OL,20,Finvestment and improved
OL,21,Finfrastructure," he said.
