OL,6,F"It also paves the way for vital
OL,7,Ftransformation of public services, and
OL,8,Fwill deliver well-deserved pay awards
OL,9,Ffor public sector workers.
OL,11,F"It is now for the Northern Ireland
OL,12,Fexecutive to use this significant
OL,13,Ffinancial package to take forward the
OL,14,Fvital work of public service
OL,15,Ftransformation and the commitment to
OL,16,Fdeliver sustainable finances `
OL,17,Fensuring better outcomes in the day-to-
OL,18,Fday lives of the people in Northern
OL,19,FIreland."
